---
pageable: true
per_page: 5
---

= partial '/partials/blog_navigation'

/ Page Header
%header.intro-header{:style => "background-image: url('/img/home-bg.jpg')"}
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2.col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
        .site-heading
          %h1 0x1BADFEED
          %hr.small/
          %span.subheading A blog about security &amp; curiosity

/ Main Content
.container
  .row
    .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2.col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
      - page_articles.each_with_index do |article, i|
        .post-preview
          = link_to article.url do
            %h2.post-title= article.title
          = article.summary
          %p.post-meta
            %span="Posted on #{article.date.strftime('%b %e')}"
        %hr/
      / Pager
      %ul.pager
        - if paginate && num_pages > 1
          - if prev_page
            %li.prev= link_to '&#8592; Newer Posts', prev_page
          - if next_page
            %li.next= link_to 'Older Posts &#8594;', next_page
%hr/
= partial '/partials/blog_footer'
